Blackouts already happening in many parts of the world 🌎 due to the energy crunch which will easily go into the 2026-2027.This is unprecedented and mainly due to the ongoing Russian war.LNG is the cleaner fuel but most nations have to turn to the dirtier fuel in COAL due to the lack of LNG supplies.Hoping for the war to end  but until then  demand for COAL will remain high.I think many people underestimate the big leap and ongoing demand in COAL.Only time will tell.

Energy hungry China 🇨🇳 are still constructing more coal power plants.This only points to one thing : COAL demand is not falling as of now.In fact  the world is becoming more reliant in coal in these uncertain times.Although the aim for the world is to go with green energy (wind  solar  hydro)   the truth is it will take years or decades for it to totally take over fossil fuel.Therefore  my stance on GEO is the same.They are flushing hard and Monday is a T+4.I have noticed big hidden hands supporting $0.375 and even $0.380. Hence - $0.375 would be good price for entry and collect when they flush the weak hands.- $0.380 if you cannot get $0.375- $0.370 would be the ultimate durians picking as this was most recent buy back done by GEO management.I see a strong recovery to come maybe even next week back to $0.4x due to the added demand that will come from 📣 that China easing from its Covid-Zero policy.This is a very strong catalyst for GEO energy as their top customer is China 🇨🇳DYODD.

XLE - Energy select sector ETF up almost 3% too on China 🇨🇳 easing its Covid-Zero policy.Naturally  Chinese demand for energy will rise as they gradually move back into full working capacity.Therefore  I have my conviction on GEO that this pull back might be the last time collect we can collect GEO at this price level  (as long as Russia war is not settled  the energy crunch will be there)Very soon  we will see more news reports on this energy crunch crisis  black out  power issues affecting many working industries and then many will see why I’m buying GEO now.PS:SGX have 2 main coal players in GEO and GEAR. Now that GEAR is delisting  the GEAR players will move to GEO and therefore the pumps can be expected to be fiercer. Food for thought.Calling all GEAR BBs to hop on the GEO express .
